ji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T04:53:03.000Z","msg":"中式: 木砧板 x2，鑊鏟，刀 x2，生鐵鑊，廚房較剪，蒸架<br />\n<br />\n西式: 刀 x 3 (santoku knife, chef's knife, pairing knife)，skillet (non-stick/ carbon steel/ stainless steel), measuring spoons &amp; cups, peeler, cutting board, strainer, sauce pan，會整甜品既買多個電子磅，sheet tray, spatular, 隔熱手套同whisk"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T05:37:56.000Z","msg":"ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我得刀得兩把，一生一熟，仲要係中式刀，西式野都係中菜刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />刀想買多把，但買多把就要換過個刀架，要鑽過牆，仲煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩個鑊、兩個煲、一個易潔鑊、一個生鐵鑊、一個醬汁鍋、一個煮麵細煲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0de236ffc5d8bb06628ff843f26ffa71f6dd2cb","tid":1998581,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T06:51:01.000Z","msg":"考慮吓蒸焗爐<br />\n可以蒸飯燉湯, 又可以焗下野食<br />\n不過缺點係有可能個爐焗野時唔夠乾, 因為佢平時蒸野有水氣<br />\n但勝在夠方便同埋慳位<br />\n利申有嵌入式焗爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n煲 - budget 幾多? 個人中意不鏽鋼&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;易潔<br />\nfissler 都幾好"},{"pid":"47dc57e1ab73bfcc8668bc3264504664aeea46b5","tid":1998581,"uid":295532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0de236ffc5d8bb06628ff843f26ffa71f6dd2cb","tid":1998581,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T06:51:01.000Z","msg":"考慮吓蒸焗爐<br />\n可以蒸飯燉湯, 又可以焗下野食<br />\n不過缺點係有可能個爐焗野時唔夠乾, 因為佢平時蒸野有水氣<br />\n但勝在夠方便同埋慳位<br />\n利申有嵌入式焗爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n煲 - budget 幾多? 個人中意不鏽鋼&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;易潔<br />\nfissler 都幾好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T10:51:34.000Z","msg":"